	<h1 class="title">「阿里 IPO」阿里巴巴的 10 个最有价值创新</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/2007/small/2007.jpg?1408114682" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">许冰清 唐云路</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-09-18 23:15:05 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/2454/medium/2454.jpg?1436651284" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


